Introduction
This Visual Studio 2019 C# calculator program will take two or one
number and one operator such as +, - , / , * , ^, %, ! and calculate
them.
Example;
1+1 =2
8 - 4=4
12 / 2 = 6
2 * 4=8
10 ^ 1 = 10
50 % 100 = 50
5 ! = 120
